OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDrizzly rain gradually petering
OL,6,Fout, then brightening up for some, but
OL,7,Fany sunshine could spark off heavy
OL,8,Fshowers. These may merge into longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain in places through this
OL,10,Fafternoon. Driest in southern coastal
OL,11,Fregions. Breezy at times. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain or showers this evening
OL,14,Fbut turning much drier from the west
OL,15,Fovernight with clear spells. Showers
OL,16,Fpossible in west Cornwall. Turning
OL,17,Fchilly in the countryside with
OL,18,Fisolated fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
